dmca.title: DMCA Violation
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

 

Please note that below-referenced copyright infringement notice does not
substantially comply with the required notification elements of the
Digital Millennium Copyright Act of 1998 ("DMCA").

 

Please note that we have not passed on the substantive merits of your
claim.

 

Please visit our web site at www.theplanet.com/index.html?p=copyright.

 

Legal Response Team

THEPLANET.COM INTERNET SERVICES, INC.


________________________________

From: Collin Kemble [mailto:collin@xenosinteractive.com] 
Posted At: Wednesday, November 15, 2006 7:39 PM
Posted To: Legal Response
Conversation: DMCA Violation
Subject: DMCA Violation


Hello,
One of your customers with the domain name, daddygoldbucks.com, and ip
address of         70.87.140.170
<http://www.networksolutions.com/whois/arin-details.jsp?parenttoken=0&wh
oistoken=2>  is currently displaying my copyrighted materials without my
permission. The materials in question are the website design itself and
the logo which were all created and copyrighted by myself. Please let me
know what I need to do to file a DMCA takedown notice with your company.
 
I can be reached at 469-438-8862. 
 
Best regards,
Collin
